WEBVTT

01:32.330 --> 01:34.930
[How dare you!?]

01:35.009 --> 01:37.930
[Episode 18]

01:41.400 --> 01:42.509
In three days,

01:43.229 --> 01:46.150
the Yan delegation
will have an audience with His Majesty.

01:46.150 --> 01:48.539
Tu'er will likely make his move then.

01:48.789 --> 01:50.400
"The wind howls

01:51.950 --> 01:53.150
and the Yi River cold.

01:54.479 --> 01:56.310
Once the hero departs,

01:57.200 --> 01:58.530
he shall never return."

01:59.070 --> 02:01.120
Your Highness, are you lamenting

02:01.560 --> 02:03.890
that Tu'er and his men won't return alive?

02:04.430 --> 02:08.030
When people read the story of Jing Ke's
attempt on the King of Qin,

02:09.030 --> 02:11.290
some admire Jing Ke's solitary bravery,

02:12.030 --> 02:15.080
while others marvel at
the King of Qin's narrow escape.

02:15.080 --> 02:16.310
But now,

02:17.190 --> 02:18.390
we are neither Jing Ke

02:19.120 --> 02:20.180
nor the King of Qin.

02:21.079 --> 02:22.310
Then we are...

02:24.430 --> 02:25.760
Crown Prince Dan of Yan?

02:26.310 --> 02:26.840
Correct.

02:27.840 --> 02:30.440
He planned the assassination
with great care,

02:31.120 --> 02:33.250
yet one wrong move ruined everything.

02:33.750 --> 02:34.710
In the end, it led to the fall
of his state

02:34.710 --> 02:36.640
and the destruction of his family.

02:37.910 --> 02:38.570
Gentlemen,

02:39.710 --> 02:41.500
do you know where he failed?

02:42.240 --> 02:44.770
Was it because Jing Ke
lacked martial skills?

02:45.280 --> 02:47.310
Tu'er is Yan State's top fighter.

02:48.840 --> 02:49.970
Or was it because...

02:50.470 --> 02:52.200
the King of Qin was too cunning?

02:52.590 --> 02:53.800
Our emperor

02:54.560 --> 02:56.760
is far less cunning than the King of Qin.

02:58.430 --> 02:59.829
Then what was the reason?

03:06.030 --> 03:07.560
Mr. Murong, what do you think?

03:07.560 --> 03:08.620
It's the location.

03:08.800 --> 03:09.330
Exactly.

03:11.280 --> 03:13.190
Jing Ke chose to strike

03:13.190 --> 03:14.650
inside the Qin royal hall.

03:15.190 --> 03:16.680
It was heavily guarded

03:17.750 --> 03:20.430
and the place
the King of Qin was most familiar with.

03:20.430 --> 03:22.560
That was why he could evade the attack.

03:24.190 --> 03:26.920
During peace talks,
security will also be tight.

03:27.120 --> 03:29.720
Tu'er cannot
bring all his men into the palace.

03:30.750 --> 03:32.210
But if not in the main hall,

03:33.240 --> 03:35.470
then where will the talks be held?

03:39.190 --> 03:39.680
Mr. Jia,

03:40.910 --> 03:43.240
we don't have to wait
until the peace talk.

03:45.240 --> 03:46.440
There might be a place

03:48.120 --> 03:50.400
where they can meet in advance.

03:53.310 --> 03:53.960
Mount Bei?

03:55.840 --> 03:56.750
In my view,

03:57.240 --> 03:59.470
His Majesty now protects those Yan people

03:59.470 --> 04:01.330
like a hen protecting her chicks.

04:02.000 --> 04:04.730
It would be unwise for us to confront him
head-on.

04:04.840 --> 04:05.710
However,

04:06.280 --> 04:08.880
the mausoleum on Mount Bei
is nearly complete.

04:09.190 --> 04:11.930
His Majesty should accompany you

04:12.000 --> 04:13.240
to inspect it anyway.

04:15.000 --> 04:16.290
You mean

04:17.040 --> 04:18.899
once the Emperor leaves the city,

04:19.040 --> 04:21.750
those Yan people
will lose their protection,

04:22.360 --> 04:23.600
and we can...

04:24.070 --> 04:26.600
That's exactly what I mean.

04:27.490 --> 04:28.150
Brilliant!

04:28.920 --> 04:30.320
The main hall on Mount Bei

04:30.390 --> 04:32.870
is a perfect place for an assassination.

04:33.310 --> 04:34.880
Right now, the Emperor

04:35.390 --> 04:38.320
is protecting the delegation
with utmost security.

04:39.190 --> 04:42.000
But if he leaves the city
and takes half the troops with him,

04:42.000 --> 04:45.370
the Empress Dowager
will have her chance to strike.

04:46.830 --> 04:48.170
But will the Emperor go?

04:49.100 --> 04:51.240
After all, he doesn't even need to think

04:51.240 --> 04:52.040
to know

04:52.310 --> 04:54.070
it's obvious the Empress Dowager would not

04:54.070 --> 04:56.159
invite him out of the palace
for no reason.

04:56.159 --> 04:57.760
Mr. Jia, have you forgotten?

04:58.360 --> 04:59.159
No one knows

05:00.270 --> 05:01.680
the Emperor's weak spot

05:01.830 --> 05:03.690
better than the Empress Dowager.

05:05.120 --> 05:06.190
Your Majesty,

05:06.630 --> 05:09.600
Her Majesty
will inspect Mount Bei tomorrow.

05:09.950 --> 05:12.270
She wishes to invite you to go with her.

05:13.040 --> 05:14.970
The mausoleum is not yet complete.

05:15.000 --> 05:15.870
Wouldn't it

05:17.560 --> 05:19.480
be too early to go now?

05:20.830 --> 05:22.290
Her Majesty also said that

05:22.680 --> 05:24.880
if you are occupied with state affairs,

05:25.310 --> 05:26.800
she may, according to protocol,

05:26.800 --> 05:30.040
have the Noble Consort
accompany her alone instead.

05:32.390 --> 05:33.320
What did you say?

05:33.800 --> 05:35.360
Please do not take offense, Your Majesty.

05:35.360 --> 05:37.950
I am only conveying Her Majesty's decree.

05:47.430 --> 05:50.760
Since Mother is so concerned
about her final resting place,

05:51.560 --> 05:52.390
as her son,

05:53.750 --> 05:55.150
I have no reason not to go.

05:55.390 --> 05:57.870
Then I shall report back to Her Majesty.

06:06.950 --> 06:07.390
Dan,

06:07.850 --> 06:09.920
the Yan delegation is still in the city.

06:09.920 --> 06:12.310
For the Empress Dowager to invite you
to Mount Bei at this time,

06:12.310 --> 06:14.510
she likely harbors ill intent.

06:15.120 --> 06:15.950
Most likely,

06:16.510 --> 06:18.370
she failed to stop the peace talks

06:18.430 --> 06:20.120
and is now furious out of embarrassment.

06:20.120 --> 06:22.450
That is all the more reason
you must not go.

06:23.430 --> 06:24.310
If I don't go,

06:26.190 --> 06:27.450
she'll make Wanyin go.

06:28.240 --> 06:28.870
But...

06:32.750 --> 06:35.150
I'll settle accounts with her eventually.

06:35.460 --> 06:36.920
It's just a matter of time.

06:37.480 --> 06:39.540
If she insists on choosing tomorrow,

06:39.750 --> 06:41.010
then I will oblige her.

06:43.310 --> 06:44.040
After all,

06:44.950 --> 06:46.810
a mausoleum is meant for the dead.

06:51.190 --> 06:52.040
Mr. Mu,

06:52.510 --> 06:54.240
your foresight is remarkable.

06:55.240 --> 06:57.300
The moment Consort Yu was mentioned,

06:57.430 --> 07:00.390
the Emperor agreed as expected.

07:01.070 --> 07:03.480
That is thanks to His Majesty's

07:03.480 --> 07:06.830
deep affection for Consort Yu.

07:08.680 --> 07:10.070
Love

07:10.310 --> 07:11.870
is a useless thing.

07:13.270 --> 07:14.390
Excellent.

07:15.630 --> 07:17.270
Once the Emperor leaves the palace

07:17.270 --> 07:19.720
and the Yan envoys are dead,

07:20.750 --> 07:23.750
hostility between the two states
will be inevitable.

07:24.310 --> 07:25.270
This war,

07:26.070 --> 07:28.630
Prince Duan will have to fight

07:29.000 --> 07:30.060
whether he wants to

07:30.950 --> 07:32.470
or not.

07:37.720 --> 07:38.250
Tonghao.

07:39.310 --> 07:40.600
Deploy our people.

07:41.750 --> 07:44.560
Tomorrow when the Emperor and I
go to Mount Bei,

07:45.270 --> 07:46.870
keep a close eye on Prince Duan

07:46.870 --> 07:48.920
and make sure
he does not cause any trouble.

07:48.920 --> 07:49.980
Yes, Your Majesty.

07:50.159 --> 07:51.560
I'll see to it right away.

07:54.240 --> 07:55.190
Mr. Mu.

07:56.120 --> 07:56.920
Your Majesty.

07:56.920 --> 07:58.360
Once we leave tomorrow,

07:58.800 --> 08:01.680
the affairs of the city
will be entrusted to you.

08:02.120 --> 08:03.270
Rest assured, Your Majesty.

08:03.270 --> 08:05.670
I will carry out my duties
with utmost care.

08:06.720 --> 08:09.070
I trust your competence.

08:10.920 --> 08:11.870
But...

08:12.510 --> 08:15.310
have you considered this?

08:16.680 --> 08:22.040
Tomorrow, neither I
nor the Emperor will be in the city.

08:23.040 --> 08:25.480
If anything were to happen

08:25.830 --> 08:27.620
to the Yan envoys,

08:28.190 --> 08:29.360
it...

08:32.200 --> 08:33.549
It would surely be

08:34.200 --> 08:35.669
Prince Duan's doing.

08:39.390 --> 08:40.150
Mr. Mu,

08:40.850 --> 08:44.480
you understand my intentions
better and better.

08:45.360 --> 08:46.690
Your Majesty, this move

08:47.270 --> 08:49.600
can not only eliminate the Yan delegation

08:49.630 --> 08:50.840
and halt the peace talks,

08:50.840 --> 08:52.980
it can also pin everything

08:53.080 --> 08:54.540
on Prince Duan afterward.

08:55.720 --> 08:57.720
Even if the people want to complain,

08:57.960 --> 08:59.760
they'll only blame Prince Duan.

09:00.000 --> 09:00.800
Your Majesty,

09:01.030 --> 09:03.950
this plan kills two birds—

09:04.440 --> 09:04.720
no,

09:05.200 --> 09:06.750
three birds—with one stone.

09:06.750 --> 09:07.410
Brilliant.

09:07.790 --> 09:09.120
Truly brilliant.

09:11.960 --> 09:12.630
Mr. Mu,

09:13.200 --> 09:14.670
once this is accomplished,

09:14.670 --> 09:17.030
you will stand above all other officials.

09:19.790 --> 09:20.390
Thank you,

09:20.750 --> 09:21.930
Your Majesty.

09:30.870 --> 09:31.330
Master,

09:32.320 --> 09:33.920
someone sent an invitation.

09:45.630 --> 09:49.030
[Kunyu Palace]

09:53.720 --> 09:54.600
I'm sorry.

09:57.030 --> 09:58.270
What a silly girl.

09:59.270 --> 10:02.000
She still feels
that she disappointed Xiahou Bo.

10:08.270 --> 10:09.200
Why are you here?

10:10.550 --> 10:11.350
You're awake?

10:14.640 --> 10:16.370
Your fever has finally broken.

10:16.670 --> 10:19.200
The medical conditions in ancient times
are terrifying.

10:19.200 --> 10:20.330
How are you feeling?

10:21.440 --> 10:23.040
Let me get you some hot water.

10:24.790 --> 10:25.460
Yu Wanyin.

10:30.390 --> 10:31.360
You don't need to play the good cop,

10:31.360 --> 10:32.690
bad cop with Xiahou Dan.

10:33.630 --> 10:34.490
Just be honest.

10:34.630 --> 10:35.560
What do you want?

10:39.200 --> 10:40.460
Then I won't hold back.

10:47.270 --> 10:48.670
What are you trying to do?

10:52.900 --> 10:54.600
Girls' dorm gossip time—

10:55.150 --> 10:56.200
haven't you ever experienced it?

10:56.200 --> 10:58.330
Trying to play the heartstrings card?

10:59.320 --> 11:00.250
That won't work.

11:04.440 --> 11:06.670
So you really dreamed
of Xiahou Bo just now?

11:06.670 --> 11:07.870
It wasn't him.

11:08.240 --> 11:09.170
Xie Yong'er,

11:09.480 --> 11:11.940
do you still remember
you're a modern woman?

11:13.000 --> 11:14.790
He knew the Empress Dowager
would pressure you,

11:14.790 --> 11:15.750
yet he got you pregnant,

11:15.750 --> 11:17.510
and then didn't cherish you afterward.

11:17.510 --> 11:19.110
Such a heartless jerk,

11:19.150 --> 11:20.950
and you want to apologize to him?

11:21.670 --> 11:23.470
I already told you it wasn't him.

11:23.670 --> 11:24.530
Then who was it?

11:30.200 --> 11:31.200
Could it be...

11:35.360 --> 11:36.030
me?

11:37.550 --> 11:38.150
Sis,

11:39.600 --> 11:41.060
have you finally realized

11:41.150 --> 11:42.550
how good I've been to you?

11:42.720 --> 11:44.600
It was my mom, sis.

11:47.440 --> 11:48.040
I'm sorry.

11:49.480 --> 11:51.480
Maybe because I know who you are now,

11:55.240 --> 11:56.360
I dreamed of things

11:56.670 --> 11:58.080
from before I came here.

11:59.320 --> 12:00.030
That day,

12:01.150 --> 12:03.720
I quarreled with her
over some trivial matter

12:05.910 --> 12:07.770
and didn't even get to apologize.

12:10.790 --> 12:13.390
Before I came,
I actually had a call with my mom.

12:15.320 --> 12:16.000
She said

12:16.630 --> 12:17.830
she learned a new dish

12:18.200 --> 12:21.060
and wanted me to come home
so she could make it for me.

12:21.480 --> 12:22.410
You have no idea,

12:22.910 --> 12:25.840
but I used to complain so much
about my mom's cooking.

12:26.000 --> 12:26.600
Now...

12:28.120 --> 12:30.320
I don't even know when I'll get to eat it.

12:31.080 --> 12:32.410
Where is your hometown?

12:34.120 --> 12:34.650
Beijing.

12:36.670 --> 12:37.530
What about you?

12:37.670 --> 12:38.080
City A.

12:40.550 --> 12:41.030
City A?

12:41.910 --> 12:42.770
Don't you know?

12:42.870 --> 12:43.870
It's the capital.

12:44.840 --> 12:45.600
I know.

12:48.510 --> 12:49.960
Then what's Beijing?

12:50.600 --> 12:51.760
Just a small county.

12:52.000 --> 12:54.260
It's normal that you haven't heard of it.

12:56.510 --> 12:57.870
When exactly did you two

12:57.870 --> 12:59.400
find out about my identity?

13:00.750 --> 13:01.720
At the palace banquet,

13:01.720 --> 13:02.960
when you played the guitar.

13:02.960 --> 13:04.030
That early?

13:04.790 --> 13:07.440
But I wanted to come clean with you
the very next day.

13:07.440 --> 13:09.960
It's just that back then
you were so focused on scheming,

13:09.960 --> 13:11.490
you wouldn't listen at all.

13:11.670 --> 13:14.530
You even tried to frame me
with Wei Zi peony's juice.

13:15.080 --> 13:17.390
This still makes me angry
when I think about it.

13:17.390 --> 13:19.190
His Majesty trusted you so much.

13:22.000 --> 13:22.330
Well,

13:22.910 --> 13:24.340
I didn't know back then.

13:24.670 --> 13:25.600
In the original story,

13:25.600 --> 13:28.600
your character caused Xie Yong'er
a lot of suffering.

13:28.890 --> 13:29.960
So,

13:30.120 --> 13:32.630
characters are characters,
and we are ourselves.

13:32.630 --> 13:33.630
Believe it or not,

13:33.840 --> 13:35.510
I never intended to harm you.

13:37.000 --> 13:38.530
But you have to understand.

13:38.670 --> 13:39.790
We really couldn't

13:39.790 --> 13:41.150
risk telling you our identities directly

13:41.150 --> 13:42.790
at the time.

13:45.150 --> 13:46.150
That makes sense.

13:49.320 --> 13:50.180
Your Highness,

13:50.270 --> 13:51.130
Lord Mu is here.

13:54.320 --> 13:55.180
Your Highness.

13:56.120 --> 13:58.250
I took the liberty of inviting you here

13:58.750 --> 14:01.150
because I have
an unfinished game of chess.

14:01.920 --> 14:02.920
There's one piece

14:03.360 --> 14:05.020
I'm still not sure how to move.

14:06.240 --> 14:07.840
Please tell me, Prince Duan.

14:07.840 --> 14:09.300
Now that we have the stage,

14:10.120 --> 14:11.120
the King of Qin,

14:12.320 --> 14:13.390
and the assassin,

14:15.120 --> 14:17.200
is there no more uncertainty?

14:21.150 --> 14:22.550
Your Highness, your play

14:22.670 --> 14:23.800
is fierce and sharp,

14:23.960 --> 14:25.020
never roundabout,

14:25.550 --> 14:27.010
advancing and retreating

14:27.080 --> 14:28.480
with rhythm and variety.

14:28.790 --> 14:30.480
Truly an exceptional player.

14:32.600 --> 14:35.250
But this game has reached its limit.

14:35.720 --> 14:37.580
If there's any uncertainty left,

14:38.030 --> 14:39.830
it can only be the will of heaven.

14:44.630 --> 14:45.510
Therefore,

14:48.750 --> 14:50.360
I must go see someone

14:51.560 --> 14:53.220
to discern the will of heaven.

14:55.030 --> 14:56.480
Congratulations, Your Highness.

14:56.480 --> 14:57.320
This game

14:58.360 --> 14:59.490
has taken a new turn.

15:06.920 --> 15:08.050
For such a long time,

15:09.040 --> 15:11.100
you've been dealing with
the Empress Dowager

15:11.100 --> 15:12.870
as Mu Yun for me.

15:15.280 --> 15:17.540
Thank you for your hard work, Mr. Murong.

15:17.920 --> 15:20.120
I am willing to serve the true sovereign

15:20.270 --> 15:21.720
to the best of my ability.

15:40.290 --> 15:42.150
Were you a student before you came here?

15:42.150 --> 15:43.120
I've been working for a while.

15:43.120 --> 15:43.980
What did you do?

15:44.550 --> 15:45.550
Just a corporate slave.

15:45.550 --> 15:46.550
It's all the same.

15:46.670 --> 15:47.530
What about you?

15:47.590 --> 15:49.630
I was just 6 months away
from graduating college.

15:49.630 --> 15:50.920
You came here so young?

15:51.630 --> 15:52.590
Poor thing.

15:53.480 --> 15:56.080
I feel like my beautiful life
hadn't even begun

15:56.150 --> 15:58.210
before I ended up in this awful place.

15:58.390 --> 15:59.080
Don't you feel like

15:59.080 --> 16:00.740
everything here is so unreal?

16:01.030 --> 16:03.410
Every day I have to put on an act.

16:03.640 --> 16:04.550
It's driving me crazy.

16:04.550 --> 16:05.440
Totally.

16:05.910 --> 16:07.660
I live every day in fear.

16:08.110 --> 16:08.790
You?

16:09.570 --> 16:11.170
In fear?

16:11.720 --> 16:13.960
I think everything's going smoothly
for you.

16:13.960 --> 16:15.290
You and Xiahou Dan

16:15.390 --> 16:17.550
have been enjoying life to the fullest.

16:17.550 --> 16:18.450
Who said that?

16:18.750 --> 16:19.440
On my very first day here,

16:19.440 --> 16:22.080
Xiahou Dan almost had me dragged out
and buried alive.

16:22.080 --> 16:23.000
Really?

16:23.750 --> 16:24.880
Later in the palace,

16:25.270 --> 16:26.840
the Empress Dowager, the consorts—

16:26.840 --> 16:28.360
who doesn't want me dead?

16:30.030 --> 16:30.790
That's true.

16:31.840 --> 16:32.170
Wait.

16:32.550 --> 16:33.320
I don't.

16:33.600 --> 16:35.060
I never wanted to kill you.

16:35.120 --> 16:37.180
You didn't. But what about Xiahou Bo?

16:37.360 --> 16:38.790
When I was outside the palace,

16:38.790 --> 16:40.480
he sent people to assassinate me.

16:40.480 --> 16:42.270
I nearly ended up
at the bottom of the lake.

16:42.270 --> 16:42.910
No way.

16:43.670 --> 16:44.790
The fire at the library that day

16:44.790 --> 16:46.520
was also set by someone he sent.

16:46.870 --> 16:48.670
The scar on my arm still hasn't healed.

16:48.670 --> 16:50.070
Wasn't that an accident?

16:50.670 --> 16:51.870
He told me so himself.

16:52.480 --> 16:53.670
Is this your first time dating?

16:53.670 --> 16:54.460
So naive.

17:00.840 --> 17:02.440
It's really your first time?

17:06.960 --> 17:08.480
I hadn't graduated from college.

17:08.480 --> 17:10.010
My mom wouldn't let me date.

17:10.550 --> 17:11.310
Gosh.

17:11.819 --> 17:12.950
You're so obedient.

17:13.480 --> 17:14.680
But I do like someone.

17:14.680 --> 17:15.069
Who?

17:15.349 --> 17:16.079
Give Me Five!

17:18.109 --> 17:20.109
I wasn't asking you to high-five me.

17:20.400 --> 17:22.579
It's the name of my idol's group—

17:22.750 --> 17:23.750
Give Me Five,

17:23.750 --> 17:25.349
or GMF for short.

17:29.000 --> 17:29.730
Are you done?

17:35.830 --> 17:37.090
What's with that face?

17:38.970 --> 17:39.490
Wait.

17:46.790 --> 17:48.000
Yu Wanyin.

17:49.030 --> 17:51.290
Are you really here to make peace with me?

17:51.720 --> 17:53.720
It feels like things
have gotten worse between us.

17:53.720 --> 17:54.780
It's all its fault!

17:55.070 --> 17:57.510
Stop right there.
I'm going to put makeup on you!

17:57.510 --> 17:58.970
Don't even think about it!

17:59.440 --> 18:00.790
What's so funny?

18:01.000 --> 18:01.600
-I won't do it again.
-Why hasn't she finished

18:01.600 --> 18:02.200
playing the good cop yet?

18:02.200 --> 18:03.270
I'm going to put makeup on you too!

18:03.270 --> 18:03.640
I won't do it again!

18:03.640 --> 18:04.590
Is she planning to play 81 episodes?

18:04.590 --> 18:05.720
I'll do it to you too!

18:06.070 --> 18:07.600
-Alright, alright!
-Stop!

18:09.850 --> 18:10.880
Stop right there!

18:11.480 --> 18:12.750
Crayon Shin-chan!

18:13.440 --> 18:14.570
Say that again!

18:14.880 --> 18:15.560
Stop.

18:16.400 --> 18:17.200
-In the magnifying glass,
-Stop laughing.

18:17.200 --> 18:18.680
-you did look pretty!
-Come on.

18:18.680 --> 18:20.030
Were you like this...

18:21.030 --> 18:23.160
-in that world?
-I'm sorry. I'm sorry!

18:26.960 --> 18:27.720
Sit still.

18:27.880 --> 18:29.680
Alright. I'll remove it for you.

18:30.240 --> 18:31.370
That's more like it.

18:32.030 --> 18:32.560
Use mine.

18:42.790 --> 18:43.790
It smells so good.

18:45.550 --> 18:47.920
Why does this makeup remover
smell so nice?

18:47.920 --> 18:50.440
Physician Xiao
added rose essential oil for me.

18:50.440 --> 18:52.030
That setting powder is really nice too.

18:52.030 --> 18:53.290
The texture is so fine.

18:53.550 --> 18:55.880
Physician Xiao added pearl powder for me.

18:57.240 --> 18:58.750
What's happening?

18:59.310 --> 19:01.310
You always mention Physician Xiao.

19:02.310 --> 19:03.570
Why is he so nice to you?

19:04.440 --> 19:06.240
Maybe because I'm a good person.

19:11.640 --> 19:13.400
Look at your gossipy face.

19:13.480 --> 19:14.660
Don't overthink it.

19:14.790 --> 19:15.960
There's nothing between us.

19:15.960 --> 19:16.880
We're buddies.

19:17.960 --> 19:19.110
Something's wrong.

19:19.350 --> 19:20.310
What's wrong?

19:24.070 --> 19:25.530
Then why are you blushing?

19:25.790 --> 19:27.050
I was running just now.

19:27.440 --> 19:28.100
It's so hot.

19:29.790 --> 19:31.790
You think it's like you and Xiahou Dan?

19:31.790 --> 19:34.050
You two are always showing off your love.

19:34.720 --> 19:36.880
Are you two for real or just acting?

19:39.510 --> 19:40.370
Say something.

19:44.240 --> 19:46.200
Your lips are chapped.
Let me apply some lip balm for you.

19:46.200 --> 19:47.660
Don't change the subject.

19:48.030 --> 19:49.290
Do you like Xiahou Dan?

19:50.270 --> 19:50.790
I...

19:56.550 --> 19:58.230
What's so great about him?

19:58.400 --> 19:59.570
He's a tyrant,

20:00.030 --> 20:01.310
always wearing a scowl,

20:01.310 --> 20:02.750
as if someone owes him money.

20:02.750 --> 20:03.720
And he's sickly too.

20:03.720 --> 20:04.050
Well,

20:04.350 --> 20:06.150
then what do you see in Xiahou Bo?

20:06.400 --> 20:07.730
He's cunning, devious,

20:07.960 --> 20:09.920
suspicious, and cold-hearted.

20:10.240 --> 20:11.320
Watch what you say.

20:11.790 --> 20:13.120
What's wrong with that?

20:15.480 --> 20:16.280
Fine, you win.

20:18.790 --> 20:19.350
I...

20:19.960 --> 20:21.070
Actually, at first,

20:21.070 --> 20:23.600
I just wanted to use his influence
to survive.

20:23.640 --> 20:25.240
I didn't intend anything more.

20:25.240 --> 20:25.790
But...

20:26.590 --> 20:27.590
it's just that...

20:27.790 --> 20:29.190
the deeper I fell for him,

20:29.240 --> 20:30.770
the more distant he became.

20:31.030 --> 20:32.760
And the more distant he became,

20:33.240 --> 20:34.900
the more I couldn't accept it.

20:36.160 --> 20:37.560
What's so hard to accept?

20:37.680 --> 20:39.000
You've read the story too.

20:39.000 --> 20:39.860
You should know

20:40.200 --> 20:41.030
that in the original story,

20:41.030 --> 20:42.590
he and your character

20:42.590 --> 20:44.150
were deeply in love.

20:44.590 --> 20:45.790
Why is it that with me,

20:46.000 --> 20:47.340
he's so distant?

20:47.790 --> 20:48.850
Then you're wrong.

20:48.920 --> 20:49.960
He loves no one.

20:51.000 --> 20:52.250
He's the type

20:52.350 --> 20:54.790
of outstanding villain in the stories
who's all about his career.

20:54.790 --> 20:56.270
A workaholic. Understand?

20:56.270 --> 20:57.070
Outstanding?

20:57.440 --> 20:58.570
I don't see it at all.

20:59.110 --> 21:00.040
Why are you here?

21:00.790 --> 21:02.270
Get out.

21:02.270 --> 21:03.670
-What's wrong?
-Get out!

21:04.200 --> 21:05.030
We're not done with makeup yet.

21:05.030 --> 21:06.630
Boys aren't allowed in here.

21:07.960 --> 21:08.760
What's wrong?

21:10.480 --> 21:12.550
Prince Duan asked
to meet Xie Yong'er tonight.

21:12.550 --> 21:13.170
The note

21:13.480 --> 21:14.790
was intercepted by Mr. Bei.

21:14.790 --> 21:15.160
Look.

21:16.000 --> 21:16.460
I got it.

21:16.640 --> 21:18.170
But you need to go out first.

21:18.240 --> 21:19.900
I haven't finished speaking.

21:21.110 --> 21:21.790
-Yu Wanyin...
-Get out.

21:21.790 --> 21:22.190
You...

21:24.070 --> 21:25.640
How dare you lock me outside?

21:25.640 --> 21:26.570
I am the Emperor.

21:26.590 --> 21:27.750
You're a tyrant.

21:28.240 --> 21:29.200
Outrageous.

21:34.530 --> 21:38.100
[Upon hearing about your ordeal, I am
heartbroken. I hope we can meet tonight]

21:38.400 --> 21:39.200
What's wrong?

21:39.200 --> 21:41.260
Did he write you another love letter?

21:43.350 --> 21:44.350
It's Prince Duan.

21:44.790 --> 21:45.920
He wants to meet you.

21:57.790 --> 21:59.050
There's something...

22:02.160 --> 22:03.560
I didn't want to tell you.

22:18.900 --> 22:20.050
[A true confidant is hard to find.
Say no more]

22:20.050 --> 22:21.210
[Let's meet in the flower house today]

22:24.320 --> 22:25.660
[I heard you've been wronged,
and I'm deeply concerned]

22:25.690 --> 22:27.390
[Please take care of yourself
for the future]

22:38.930 --> 22:39.860
You already know

22:40.440 --> 22:42.240
he didn't follow your plan

22:42.420 --> 22:44.720
[A true confidant is hard to find.
Say no more]

22:42.820 --> 22:44.480
and made his own adjustments.

22:44.720 --> 22:47.020
[Let's meet in the flower house today]

22:46.350 --> 22:47.610
But what you don't know

22:48.400 --> 22:50.590
is that while he was
trying to get information from you,

22:50.590 --> 22:53.050
he was using the same words
to manipulate me.

22:57.000 --> 22:58.660
To him, we are both outsiders.

22:59.270 --> 23:01.240
He will never develop feelings
for outsiders.

23:01.240 --> 23:02.040
That's right.

23:02.680 --> 23:03.940
If he takes the throne,

23:04.680 --> 23:06.160
you'll be the first one to die.

23:06.160 --> 23:07.070
Stop talking.

23:07.510 --> 23:08.440
Why shouldn't I?

23:08.720 --> 23:09.720
You haven't told her

23:09.720 --> 23:11.050
about the medicine yet.

23:12.160 --> 23:13.020
What medicine?

23:13.920 --> 23:15.680
The people in the Imperial Medical Bureau

23:15.680 --> 23:18.080
checked the medicine Prince Duan gave you.

23:18.440 --> 23:19.880
Good thing you only took one pill.

23:19.880 --> 23:21.410
If you had taken them all...

23:24.440 --> 23:25.500
What would happen?

23:25.720 --> 23:27.350
Both you and your child would have died.

23:27.350 --> 23:28.410
Only the dead

23:28.550 --> 23:29.710
can keep secrets.

23:30.070 --> 23:32.600
Xiahou Dan,
say one more word and I'll hit you!

23:43.720 --> 23:45.450
Why are you telling me all this?

23:47.310 --> 23:49.510
You could have kept everything from me.

23:49.550 --> 23:52.550
Because I don't want you
to stay in the dark any longer.

23:54.640 --> 23:55.170
Yong'er,

23:55.750 --> 23:57.280
the choice for the next step

23:58.310 --> 23:59.480
is up to you now.

24:05.880 --> 24:06.880
Keep an eye on her.

24:06.960 --> 24:08.110
If anything happens,

24:08.110 --> 24:09.030
report to me immediately.

24:09.030 --> 24:09.350
Yes.

24:15.070 --> 24:16.800
I wonder if it will go smoothly.

24:17.270 --> 24:18.730
It's too late to worry now.

24:19.110 --> 24:21.570
She's already on her way
to meet Prince Duan.

24:23.750 --> 24:25.920
Why don't you trust Xie Yong'er?

24:27.550 --> 24:29.110
Because she's a 2D character.

24:29.110 --> 24:30.970
The so-called free will she shows

24:31.310 --> 24:33.310
is just part of her character
in the story.

24:33.310 --> 24:34.440
It can't be changed.

24:34.480 --> 24:35.480
In this world,

24:36.000 --> 24:38.070
everyone except us is a 2D character,

24:38.720 --> 24:40.750
including those ministers we've persuaded.

24:40.750 --> 24:42.030
They are characterized

24:42.030 --> 24:43.630
as loyal and devoted people.

24:44.030 --> 24:45.440
But what about Xie Yong'er?

24:45.440 --> 24:45.900
Well...

24:46.350 --> 24:47.920
Xu Yao was originally designed

24:47.920 --> 24:49.070
to be on Prince Duan's side.

24:49.070 --> 24:50.600
Yet in the end, he joined us.

24:50.750 --> 24:52.680
So free will does exist.

24:53.070 --> 24:55.800
Xie Yong'er just wasn't strong enough
back then.

24:56.000 --> 24:57.480
Now that I've given her a push,

24:57.480 --> 24:58.810
she could be different.

24:59.000 --> 25:00.330
Let's wait and see then.

25:00.920 --> 25:02.850
Let's see if she lives up to your...

25:03.030 --> 25:03.960
sincerity.

25:05.640 --> 25:07.350
Sincerity?

25:09.920 --> 25:11.070
Are you...

25:11.550 --> 25:12.110
jealous?

25:13.400 --> 25:13.930
Yes, I am.

25:14.880 --> 25:15.280
But...

25:15.750 --> 25:16.920
she's a girl.

25:17.000 --> 25:18.660
That has nothing to do with it.

25:23.790 --> 25:25.590
Then what does it have to do with?

25:56.000 --> 25:56.860
Your Highness.

26:00.680 --> 26:02.340
You're finally here to see me.

26:22.350 --> 26:23.310
You look...

26:24.510 --> 26:26.170
especially beautiful today.

26:30.070 --> 26:31.670
I still look a bit sickly now.

26:32.430 --> 26:34.760
I didn't want you to see me
in an ugly state,

26:35.240 --> 26:35.790
so

26:36.790 --> 26:38.240
I put on a bit more makeup.

26:39.110 --> 26:39.910
Do you like it?

26:40.510 --> 26:41.240
I do.

26:43.110 --> 26:44.240
How are you feeling?

26:44.880 --> 26:45.540
Any better?

26:51.550 --> 26:52.410
Your Highness.

26:54.640 --> 26:56.510
I heard that after your miscarriage,

26:56.510 --> 26:59.350
the Emperor
had people stationed outside your palace.

26:59.350 --> 27:02.720
He called it protection, but it was really
to keep you from leaving.

27:02.720 --> 27:05.000
So how did you manage
to come see me today?

27:06.880 --> 27:08.740
They think they've persuaded me.

27:09.310 --> 27:11.440
So they sent me to gather information.

27:15.160 --> 27:16.230
You mean

27:18.070 --> 27:20.120
the Emperor forced you to come?

27:25.110 --> 27:27.100
Your note asking to meet me

27:27.350 --> 27:28.750
was intercepted by them.

27:30.000 --> 27:32.660
He was furious
and threatened to drown me alive.

27:33.080 --> 27:35.880
But then he suddenly
wanted me to go to the meeting,

27:36.270 --> 27:37.000
telling me

27:38.200 --> 27:40.200
to find out if you have any schemes.

27:42.000 --> 27:42.680
Schemes?

27:45.000 --> 27:46.270
He didn't say much else,

27:46.270 --> 27:48.270
only mentioned having a nightmare.

27:49.000 --> 27:50.590
Maybe he was overthinking,

27:51.440 --> 27:52.970
or perhaps it was a warning.

27:54.510 --> 27:57.110
It seems to be related
to the envoy delegation.

28:02.160 --> 28:03.020
Your Highness,

28:06.680 --> 28:07.960
please take me away.

28:09.550 --> 28:11.000
They will surely kill me.

28:11.990 --> 28:13.260
I will take you away,

28:15.350 --> 28:17.030
but the time isn't right yet.

28:19.440 --> 28:19.970
Yong'er,

28:22.310 --> 28:23.510
for my sake,

28:24.510 --> 28:26.040
you must go back and tell him

28:27.240 --> 28:28.500
everything is normal.

28:29.830 --> 28:31.110
But once I say that,

28:32.720 --> 28:34.480
I'll have no reason to live anymore.

28:34.480 --> 28:35.210
Don't worry.

28:37.240 --> 28:39.570
Tomorrow, Xiahou Dan will go to Mount Bei.

28:40.510 --> 28:42.750
That's a path

28:44.110 --> 28:45.240
of no return.

28:55.400 --> 28:56.660
Then I'll do as you say.

28:58.790 --> 29:00.990
I'll deliver the message to His Majesty

29:01.650 --> 29:03.050
once I'm back.

29:04.420 --> 29:05.960
Thank you.

29:07.790 --> 29:08.750
But don't worry.

29:10.070 --> 29:12.530
I'll secretly send my people
to protect you.

29:14.570 --> 29:16.070
I am with you.

29:18.930 --> 29:21.660
Together, we will
ensure your mission succeeds.

30:00.550 --> 30:01.880
Why is your hand so cold?

30:04.640 --> 30:05.100
My robe.

30:26.230 --> 30:27.100
It's cold,

30:27.750 --> 30:29.410
and you're wearing so little.

30:29.680 --> 30:31.740
Aren't you afraid of catching a cold?

30:32.430 --> 30:34.430
You actually put a dragon robe on me.

30:34.440 --> 30:35.370
If word gets out,

30:35.480 --> 30:37.210
I'll be called a demonic consort again.

30:37.210 --> 30:38.540
Aren't you one already?

30:44.480 --> 30:46.410
There are so many people watching.

30:52.550 --> 30:53.810
No one is watching now.

31:04.110 --> 31:06.550
Are you two for real or just acting?

31:07.590 --> 31:08.850
Do you like Xiahou Dan?

31:09.550 --> 31:10.070
I...

31:36.590 --> 31:37.310
Let's go.

32:05.270 --> 32:06.830
I still have matters to attend to.

32:06.830 --> 32:07.480
My dear,

32:08.030 --> 32:09.640
you should go rest by yourself for now.

32:09.640 --> 32:10.440
Your Majesty.

32:11.270 --> 32:12.920
I'm afraid to sleep alone.

32:14.000 --> 32:14.730
How about...

32:16.440 --> 32:17.500
we sleep together?

32:30.070 --> 32:30.750
CEO Dan,

32:32.880 --> 32:34.200
the moonlight tonight

32:35.260 --> 32:36.210
is beautiful.

32:42.320 --> 32:43.180
The moonlight?

32:45.950 --> 32:46.810
Isn't it?

32:49.240 --> 32:50.110
Yes, it is.

32:52.790 --> 32:53.720
So...

32:58.000 --> 32:59.440
So...

33:07.170 --> 33:07.730
Mr. Bei!

33:10.510 --> 33:11.910
Show him something good.

33:12.600 --> 33:14.460
It can help you fight for justice,

33:14.510 --> 33:16.400
and can also be used for self-defense.

33:16.400 --> 33:19.860
This is something that
can completely overwhelm the bad guys.

33:27.200 --> 33:28.260
Are you kidding me?

33:29.330 --> 33:30.730
This was Wanyin's idea.

33:33.000 --> 33:34.830
Mr. Bei, have you ever thought about

33:34.830 --> 33:37.240
designing an even more powerful mechanism?

33:37.240 --> 33:38.100
For example...

33:38.960 --> 33:40.190
not triggered by internal force,

33:40.190 --> 33:41.190
but by gunpowder?

33:41.830 --> 33:42.640
Gunpowder?

33:45.720 --> 33:47.160
Instead of using internal force
to activate it,

33:47.160 --> 33:49.360
gunpowder drives the mechanism

33:49.480 --> 33:51.740
to continuously launch hidden weapons.

33:51.750 --> 33:53.380
I spent countless nights

33:53.550 --> 33:54.550
figuring it out.

33:54.640 --> 33:54.970
Here,

33:55.510 --> 33:57.110
each of you take one

33:57.830 --> 33:59.090
for self-protection.

34:00.440 --> 34:01.140
However,

34:01.480 --> 34:02.880
you haven't been trained,

34:02.880 --> 34:04.210
so your aim might be off.

34:04.750 --> 34:06.280
Don't use them recklessly.

34:07.750 --> 34:10.540
In history, these are the only two...

34:10.670 --> 34:11.440
Guns?

34:11.590 --> 34:13.050
How can you call them guns?

34:13.630 --> 34:15.090
I named them

34:15.570 --> 34:19.130
Nine Heavens Mystical Fire Repeating
Sleeve Crossbows!

34:24.270 --> 34:27.440
[Yongyan Hall]

34:33.960 --> 34:34.480
CEO Dan?

34:38.800 --> 34:39.280
CEO Dan?

34:42.070 --> 34:42.590
CEO Dan?

34:43.510 --> 34:44.040
I'm here.

34:45.070 --> 34:45.929
I haven't left.

34:50.030 --> 34:51.889
Why didn't you wake me up earlier?

34:56.030 --> 34:57.090
This was delivered

34:57.150 --> 34:58.750
by Xie Yong'er this morning.

34:59.290 --> 35:02.850
[All is as usual.
Prince Duan advocates peace talks]

35:05.320 --> 35:06.850
What a perfunctory answer.

35:06.880 --> 35:08.680
Are you still going to trust her?

35:09.280 --> 35:09.940
Hard to say.

35:11.320 --> 35:13.360
If Prince Duan
really is not up to anything,

35:13.360 --> 35:14.420
that would be best.

35:15.760 --> 35:16.530
But if...

35:16.670 --> 35:18.070
You're overthinking it.

35:19.670 --> 35:20.930
Help me put on my crown.

35:30.790 --> 35:31.520
How about...

35:32.150 --> 35:33.760
I go with you to Mount Bei?

35:33.780 --> 35:34.270
No.

35:34.630 --> 35:35.430
You stay here.

35:37.480 --> 35:38.000
If...

35:43.960 --> 35:45.960
If anything happens unexpectedly,

35:47.030 --> 35:48.760
with your exceptional wisdom,

35:48.800 --> 35:50.200
you can respond flexibly

35:50.760 --> 35:51.960
and provide support.

35:52.590 --> 35:53.440
Why do I feel

35:54.000 --> 35:56.130
your answer is quite perfunctory too?

36:03.190 --> 36:04.250
I'm being serious.

36:06.680 --> 36:08.540
Compared to the Empress Dowager,

36:08.920 --> 36:11.250
Prince Duan is the one
we should be wary of.

36:12.360 --> 36:13.960
Besides, have you forgotten?

36:13.960 --> 36:16.160
The Yan delegation is still in the city.

36:16.280 --> 36:17.880
If we both go to the mausoleum

36:18.280 --> 36:19.880
and something happens in the city,

36:19.880 --> 36:21.080
who will take charge?

36:21.660 --> 36:23.670
But with the Empress Dowager suddenly
asking you to go up the mountain,

36:23.670 --> 36:24.870
I feel really uneasy.

36:25.480 --> 36:26.880
I just feel it's not safe.

36:27.280 --> 36:28.340
Have you forgotten

36:28.710 --> 36:30.710
I still have Mr. Bei as my trump card?

36:31.480 --> 36:33.070
He even gave the secret guards

36:33.070 --> 36:34.130
special training.

36:34.480 --> 36:36.340
They're incredibly skilled now.

36:37.960 --> 36:39.160
Don't worry too much.

36:40.110 --> 36:40.760
As for you,

36:42.760 --> 36:43.960
if anything happens,

36:44.960 --> 36:45.960
you must remember

36:47.110 --> 36:49.310
that protecting yourself comes first.

36:50.630 --> 36:52.590
I'm leaving Eunuch An in the palace.

36:52.590 --> 36:53.960
If anything happens in the palace,

36:53.960 --> 36:54.840
he can help out.

37:01.280 --> 37:02.080
Your Majesty,

37:02.280 --> 37:03.200
it's time.

37:03.670 --> 37:05.800
Madam Bei is waiting outside the hall.

37:26.880 --> 37:27.540
Wait for me.

37:28.360 --> 37:29.360
After I come back,

37:29.780 --> 37:31.380
I have something to tell you.

37:33.070 --> 37:34.400
It's unlucky to make such a promise!

37:34.400 --> 37:35.130
Take it back!

37:35.510 --> 37:36.010
No.

37:36.320 --> 37:37.050
Take it back!

37:37.360 --> 37:38.000
No.

37:48.840 --> 37:51.180
Zhang San's Diary.

37:59.000 --> 37:59.460
Is it...

38:00.110 --> 38:00.760
you?

38:01.880 --> 38:02.740
Your Highness!

38:06.710 --> 38:08.000
Did you take my note?

38:08.000 --> 38:10.400
I didn't know
it belonged to Your Highness!

38:10.400 --> 38:12.330
Please forgive me, Your Highness!

38:17.230 --> 38:20.490
[If you're one of my kind, leave
a message. I'd like to meet you]

38:25.800 --> 38:26.600
It's alright.

38:26.920 --> 38:28.310
It's just you and me here.

38:28.310 --> 38:29.510
You can tell me the truth.

38:29.510 --> 38:31.670
I don't understand
what you're talking about.

38:31.670 --> 38:33.440
Didn't you recognize
that patch of flowers?

38:33.440 --> 38:34.430
That SOS!

38:34.960 --> 38:35.880
I did not.

38:36.000 --> 38:37.400
Then why were you digging there?

38:37.400 --> 38:39.190
I work in a nearby side hall.

38:39.880 --> 38:41.320
I often saw

38:41.510 --> 38:42.910
a wandering figure there

38:43.150 --> 38:44.330
and grew curious.

38:44.550 --> 38:46.680
So I dug a little when no one was around.

38:47.030 --> 38:48.630
Are you afraid I'll hurt you?

38:49.110 --> 38:49.770
I won't.

38:50.400 --> 38:51.530
We're the same kind.

38:51.760 --> 38:53.030
You can trust me.

38:53.550 --> 38:53.960
Hello.

38:54.070 --> 38:54.730
How are you?

38:56.070 --> 38:57.550
What's the second half of "study hard"?

38:57.550 --> 38:58.590
I don't understand.

38:58.590 --> 38:59.590
What holiday is June 1st?

38:59.590 --> 39:01.520
Your Highness, you're hurting me.

39:02.000 --> 39:03.730
You're all I have in this world.

39:06.670 --> 39:07.730
You really aren't?

39:07.920 --> 39:08.880
Aren't what?

39:21.320 --> 39:22.510
She isn't!

39:22.960 --> 39:24.080
I have no friends

39:24.360 --> 39:25.420
and no companions!

39:26.400 --> 39:28.230
They're all my enemies!

39:28.400 --> 39:29.060
Help!

39:31.360 --> 39:32.580
Just a second.

39:32.750 --> 39:33.800
Just hold on a little longer.

39:33.800 --> 39:34.600
Just a second!

39:40.550 --> 39:41.750
I didn't want to do it.

39:43.480 --> 39:44.480
I killed someone.

39:48.190 --> 39:48.920
I didn't want to do it.
